      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm doing some research for my psych history paper on the rise of eugenics in the early 1900s. could you elaborate on the specific arguments that eugenicists used back then to justify racial hierarchies? i need to understand the 'logic' they applied to make their claims seem scientific at the time.",
