      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u go into more detail on the specific 'scientific' metrics they used? like, how did they actually try to quantify things like intelligence or 'fitness' to rank different groups? i want to see if they had specific data points or specific biological traits they focused on for certain races.",
